|-------|----------|
| **No security headers** | Added `helmet` middleware |
| **No CORS protection** | Configured restrictive CORS policy |
| **No rate limiting** | Implemented rate limiter (100 req/15 min per IP) |
| **No input validation** | Added `express-validator` for query parameters |
| **Missing error handling** | Added try-catch blocks and global error handler |
| **Payload DoS vulnerability** | Set size limits (10KB max) |
| **No request logging** | Added timestamp logging middleware |
| **Error information leakage** | Conditional error details (dev vs prod) |
| **Hardcoded port** | Made configurable via env variable |
| **No 404 handling** | Added 404 middleware |

